cross: Paphiopedilum President Fred x Paphiopedilum Magically Wood

measurements.description: One full flower on one sturdy 19.0-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal white, veined green-brown, overlaid green basal one-third, transitioning to deep rose marginal two-thirds; synsepal green, burgundy stripes, edge rose; petals green basally transitioning to deep rose marginally, heavy dark mahogany warts basal two-thirds, upper margin hirsute; pouch burgundy, veined darker burgundy; staminode pale green, darker green centrally; substance medium; texture waxy.
